| 4.1 Read the ‚ÄúCluster Configuration‚Äù document. | Cluster Configuration | 3372 e313e78f-6ed9-4137-8e36-fe5db1ebfbe4 complete | Brief explanation with an example. Good to have further reading links. As a person who has tried to configure a multi task job cluster, I think our detailed documentations and videos are great but we are lacking a compact guideline with an example along with a couple of main arguments. Because it can be difficult to estimate what argument is required with what parameter and the impact. |
